flowchart LR
    A[Reasoning item] --> B[Collect diffusion trajectories]
    B --> C[Checkpoint intermediate states]
    C --> D{Final answer correct?}
    D -->|No| E[Oracle repair probe]
    D -->|Yes| F[Negative-repair probe]
    E --> G[Correction-rate curve]
    E --> H[Top-k repairable checkpoint labels]
    C --> I[State features]
    I --> J[Repairability predictor]
    H --> J
    J --> K[Selected repair checkpoint]
    K --> L[Expected repaired pass@k]
    F --> M[Negative repair rate]
    G --> N[Gain curves and best-step histograms]
    L --> O[Aggregate tables]
    M --> O
    N --> O
